<p>Today we introduce the dark mode to your documentations! Depending on your system settings, your page will appear in a light mode (default) or in a darker scheme.</p>

<p>You‚Äôll also be able to toggle to light or dark mode regarding your own preferences.</p>

<p>We hope you will enjoy the new experience. üëª</p>

