            <div class="tag-list">
                <a class="label" data-label-status="inverted">Improvement</a>
            </div>
            <p><img src="/images/updates/verbs-in-nav.png" alt="verbs-in-navigation-zoom.png" /></p>

<p>Displaying operations in an endpoint or a channel is sometimes not enough. 
You can now configure your documentations to show operation verbs in navigation.</p>

<p>To enable it, go to your documentation settings ‚ÄúCustomize UI‚Äù tab, then select ‚ÄúGroups and operations with verbs‚Äù in the ‚ÄúNavigation‚Äù input.</p>

